{"tid":1727065,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【環境衛生JJ入】集思廣益， Connect世衛？","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T11:44:50.000Z","uid":44556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"82bd9105944baa5f05ee582582cf666074736649","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:19:43.000Z","msg":"如TLDR，我只想問一件事：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇可能用Dioxin contamination（二噁英污染）為題去搵世衛向港共政府施壓？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n致Mon Po狗：除非你與家人不在香港，你亦絕不可能到TG區域，否則<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議你們加入，否則你的下一代必一同攬炒。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n正文：<br />\n<br />\n我諗好多巴絲都聽過大陸製TG造成嘅二噁英污染。<br />\n如果想要多少少背景，可以睇吓K Kwong呢段片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=453229281998561&amp;id=179179469403545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D453229281998561%26id%3D179179469403545&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQNG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=2a3af505\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=453229281998561&amp;id=179179469403545</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大陸TG嘅危害已經開始見到，最明顯一定喺中大嘅動物開始相繼死亡：<br />\n<br />\n鳥類：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/applepetform/專題/detail/1_60267228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fapplepetform%2F%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2Fdetail%2F1_60267228&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQNG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=87a518d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fapplepetform%2F%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2Fdetail%2F1_60267228&h=b68ffa71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/applepetform/專題/detail/1_60267228</a><br />\n<br />\n松鼠：<br />\n（搵唔返link，圖為沙田美林有松鼠死亡，疑因TG中毒，有LINK歡迎補上）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二噁英喺好多年前已被證實對人類影響極大，包括致癌及影響生殖系統等等，禍延下一代。<br />\n<br />\nWHO其實都有出過一啲Paper同Programme去監察同raise public concern on dioxin contamination.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/dioxins-and-their-effects-on-human-health\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fdioxins-and-their-effects-on-human-health&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQNG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=30559d26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/dioxins-and-their-effects-on-human-health</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多，有咩可以諗吓喺香港做？：<br />\n<br />\n1) 當務之急喺<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搵方法探查曾被TG放題地區嘅二噁英濃度</span></span>。首當其衝是中大，其餘幾間曾被放題的大專院校，以及經常被射的市區（黃大仙，將軍澳，油尖旺等）。<br />\nSampling包括泥土、地面、建築、當區林木等等。（小弟非專業，歡迎補充）<br />\n<br />\n2）搵人 / 搵Lab去做化驗。<br />\n<br />\n3）出咗result如果喺significant，要搵人去做report交俾WHO，帶出<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸TG喺Dioxin contamination嘅一個major factor</span></span>。要推出國際<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由國際組織</span></span>向政府施壓，停用TG。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上三點實施起嚟嘅難度：<br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"font-size: large;\">Sampling要人力物力。</span>同埋做Sampling嘅人要冒一定風險。要減低風險，最好有資源提供<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全套保護裝備</span></span>俾佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n2) 做testing / lab好貴亦唔容易搵。（WHO網頁寫呢類Screening一次要1000USD？我唔熟，求補充）<br />\n<br />\n3) 出Paper要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搵專業團隊</span></span>去做。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，希望巴絲講吓可唔可行，有冇團隊可以做到等等。<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n- 其實某啲區域嘅Dioxin /ppm喺升咗：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/psLZCGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpsLZCGW.jpg&h=870a40b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-- from K Kwong Facebook<br />\n<br />\n- 有人提議種菇 / 種細菌去分解 / 吸走二噁英：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157594771732158&amp;id=11383432157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157594771732158%26id%3D11383432157&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQNG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=92e3a6e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157594771732158&amp;id=11383432157</a><br />\n-- Also from K Kwong Facebook"},{"pid":"1716f9b34b20b1cdcd8c7abd5489b4c07aa7f3eb","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"為表誠意，自推10次<br />\n<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"efb0a8b26d02facd255ee3f39c22e5d8470b8179","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a6c64798139465d5d72a34563b95d55a281054b2","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:20:35.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234d6218187274a5ced91c51f1d2f8afbaf0a8f4","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439c6bce75928a3b652d6fcff94ad27969487f6f","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:19.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3683db652a49ec79e3964447a2a03d892af10250","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人加入討論"},{"pid":"33a132cc830143c0f94e270b4b7222d8064d078f","tid":1727065,"uid":44556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf568a862fa21b3d3ccaf70a39de7cc31480ee3",